title: Bosa getting to QB but annoyed he doesn’t have more sacks
text:
Posted: 1:03 p.m. Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 Bosa getting to QB but annoyed he doesn’t have more sacks Staff Writer COLUMBUS — 
Joey Bosa hasn’t shrugged much this season, and when he recorded his first official solo sack Saturday against Maryland, his famous celebratory shrug lasted as long as a blink. 
Perhaps Bosa will save a grander shrug for a bigger moment. This one came in the midst of a 49-28 victory. Continue Reading Read the complete story...
